{"blocks":[{"key":"dteur","text":"Replace inoculation loop (after step I in the below figure) and dilute across the plate","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"2u5u9","text":"Transfer 5 ml of LB broth into a universal tube","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
